item.title: I Registered My Server Yesterday
item.dc:creator: @deathschaos9 DeathsChaos9
item.description:
@deathschaos9 wrote:

The best way to do it, and it does work, trust me. When they give you the user and pass, go make that account. Than get off the account, go into the character file, and change the connectedFrom to the IP address it gives you. Works every time for me.
